'''克雷格·史蒂芬·懷特'''（{{lang-en|Craig Steven Wright}}，{{bd|1970年|10月}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://companydb.uk/08260048-denariuz-ltd |title=Denariuz Ltd 08260048 company information |date=2015 |publisher=Company Database UK |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222145241/http://companydb.uk/08260048-denariuz-ltd |dead-url=no }}</ref>），澳大利亞電腦科學家、商人與自稱<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.economist.com/news/business-and-finance/21698060-craig-wright-reveals-himself-as-satoshi-nakamoto |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825235308/http://www.economist.com/news/business-and-finance/21698060-craig-wright-reveals-himself-as-satoshi-nakamoto |dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[比特幣|比特幣]]發明者[[中本聰|中本聰]]假名的背後真實人物<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-36168863 |title=Creator of Bitcoin digital cash reveals identity |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2018-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107035542/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-36168863 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年12月，《[[連線|連線]]》與''[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]]''分別進行調查，認為懷特可能就是比特幣的發明者<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.wired.com/2015/12/bitcoins-creator-satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-this-unknown-australian-genius/ | title=Bitcoin's Creator Satoshi Nakamoto Is Probably This Unknown Australian Genius | work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] | date=December 8, 2015 | accessdate=December 8, 2015 | last1=Greenberg | first1=Andy | last2=Branwen | first2=Gwern | archive-date=2015-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210025320/http://www.wired.com/2015/12/bitcoins-creator-satoshi-nakamoto-is-probably-this-unknown-australian-genius/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://gizmodo.com/this-australian-says-he-and-his-dead-friend-invented-bi-1746958692 | title=This Australian Says He and His Dead Friend Invented Bitcoin | publisher=[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] | date=December 8, 2015 | accessdate=December 8, 2015 | last1=Biddle | first1=Sam | last2=Cush | first2=Andy | archive-date=2020-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129042458/https://gizmodo.com/this-australian-says-he-and-his-dead-friend-invented-bi-1746958692 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而在隨後的報導當中，嚴重懷疑懷特正在進行一場精心的騙局<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/2015/12/new-clues-suggest-satoshi-suspect-craig-wright-may-be-a-hoaxer/ |title=New Clues Suggest Craig Wright, Suspected Bitcoin Creator, May Be a Hoaxer |work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] |date=11 December 2015 |first=Andy |last=Greenberg |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030945/https://www.wired.com/2015/12/new-clues-suggest-satoshi-suspect-craig-wright-may-be-a-hoaxer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newyorker.com/business/currency/bizarre-saga-craig-wright-latest-inventor-bitcoin |publisher=''[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]'' |first=Maria |last=Bustillos |title=The Bizarre Saga of Craig Wright, the Latest “Inventor of Bitcoin” |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108120408/http://www.newyorker.com/business/currency/bizarre-saga-craig-wright-latest-inventor-bitcoin |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/sgi-denies-links-with-alleged-bitcoin-founder-craig-wright/ |title=SGI denies links with alleged bitcoin founder Craig Wright |publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]] |date=11 December 2015 |first=Aimee |last=Chanthadavong |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095755/https://www.zdnet.com/article/sgi-denies-links-with-alleged-bitcoin-founder-craig-wright/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在《連線》出版這份報導的數小時後，懷特位於新南威爾斯州{{le|高登 (新南威爾斯州)|Gordon, New South Wales|高登}}的家，以及位於雪梨[[賴德市|賴德市]]的相關營業場所，皆遭到[[澳大利亞聯邦警察|澳大利亞聯邦警察]]的搜索<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnet.com/au/news/bitcoin-whodunit-leads-to-oz/ |title=Bitcoin whodunit leads to Oz |publisher=[[CNET|CNET]] |first=Carrie |last=Mihalcik |date=10 December 2015 |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831211933/https://www.cnet.com/au/news/bitcoin-whodunit-leads-to-oz/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-35048309 |title='Bitcoin founder's' Australia home raided by Sydney police |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=9 December 2015 |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108162609/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-35048309 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Police Raid Sydney Home of Man Who Reportedly Created Bitcoin |work=[[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]] |date=9 December 2015 |first1=Edward |last1=Johnson |first2=Angus |last2=Whitley |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-09/police-raid-sydney-home-of-man-who-reportedly-created-bitcoin |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111204602/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-09/police-raid-sydney-home-of-man-who-reportedly-created-bitcoin |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-australia-bitcoin-exclusive-idUSKBN0TS0AB20151209 |title=Australian police raid Sydney home of reported bitcoin creator |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |first=Byron |last=Kaye |date=9 December 2015 |accessdate=2016-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110233127/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-australia-bitcoin-exclusive-idUSKBN0TS0AB20151209 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據警方說法，此次搜查是{{le|澳大利亞稅務局|Australian Taxation Office}}偵查行動的一部份<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/dec/09/bitcoin-founder-craig-wrights-home-raided-by-australian-police | title=Reported bitcoin 'founder' Craig Wright's home raided by Australian police | publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=December 8, 2015 | accessdate=December 8, 2015 | last1=Hunt | first1=Elle | last2=Farrell | first2=Paul | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108164601/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/dec/09/bitcoin-founder-craig-wrights-home-raided-by-australian-police | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/news/bitcoin-mystery-home-of-man-believed-to-be-currency-founder-raided/story-fni0cx4q-1227639557901 | title=Bitcoin mystery: Home of man believed to be currency founder raided | publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | date=December 9, 2015 | accessdate=December 9, 2015}}</ref>。

2016年5月2日，懷特自己公開透露，他就是比特幣的創始者。此次說法是在{{le|比特幣基金會|Bitcoin Foundation}}創始總監喬恩·馬特尼斯（{{lang|en|Jon Matonis}}）的部落格文章中證實<ref>{{cite web | url=http://themonetaryfuture.blogspot.no/2016/05/how-i-met-satoshi.html | title=How I Met Satoshi | publisher=The Monetary Future | date=May 2, 2016 | accessdate=2016-05-02 | archive-date=2018-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511013654/http://themonetaryfuture.blogspot.no/2016/05/how-i-met-satoshi.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，當中記載「在我存有的加密證據顯示，克雷格使用了從#1區與#9區新生成的錢幣，簽署並認證了一段訊息（第一次交易給[[哈爾·芬尼|哈爾·芬尼]]〔{{lang|en|Hal Finney}}〕）。」但后来有人指出怀特只是把一个著名比特币交易中的签名数据直接复制出来了而已，而比特币的所有交易訊息（尤其是数位签名）本来就是完全公开的，把本就是公开的数字签名复制粘贴一遍这种事情任何人都可以做到，所以无法证明他是中本聪。<ref>{{cite web|title=为什么说这个中本聪是假的，至少也是没证据证明他是真的。_申屠青春_新浪博客|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_a18a54310102wieu.html|date=2016-05-04|accessdate=2019-02-27|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228004539/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_a18a54310102wieu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最關鍵證明是匯入比特幣至2009年的比特幣第一筆交易地址，該地址被視為是中本聰所有，並要求表演匯回，BBC記者將0.017個比特幣匯入，但最終沒有匯回。之後克雷格宣布放棄證明自己是中本聪，並發表了一篇顧左右而言他的部落格文章。

2018Deconomy会议期间主办了一个叫“Bitcoin, Controversy over Principle”的座谈会，邀请了曾自称是比特币创始人中本聪的澳大利亚人 Craig Wright 做了主题 Lightning Network 演讲，被[[以太坊|以太坊]]创始人 Vitalik Buterin 称为骗子。<ref>{{cite web|title=Deconomy 2018 Heats Up|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TglmWKJBTec|date=2018-04-03|accessdate=2018-04-04|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121115004/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TglmWKJBTec|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[闪电網路|闪电網路]]作者指出他的演讲不知所云。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ethereum Founder Confronts Self-Proclaimed Bitcoin Creator Craig Wright, Calls Him a Fraud - Slashdot|url=https://slashdot.org/story/18/04/03/1947222/ethereum-founder-confronts-self-proclaimed-bitcoin-creator-craig-wright-calls-him-a-fraud|website=slashdot.org|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-04|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033351/https://slashdot.org/story/18/04/03/1947222/ethereum-founder-confronts-self-proclaimed-bitcoin-creator-craig-wright-calls-him-a-fraud|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年8月26日，懷特因涉嫌伪造合約，将{{en-link|戴夫·克萊曼|Dave Kleiman}}资产和公司转让给自己<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-28/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-says-fortune-inaccessible |title=Self-Proclaimed Bitcoin Inventor Says Fortune Inaccessible |accessdate=2019-08-29 |archive-date=2020-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523172552/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-28/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-says-fortune-inaccessible |dead-url=no }}</ref>，被[[美国佛罗里达南区联邦地区法院|美国佛罗里达南区联邦地区法院]]判決懷特须将持有的50%的[[比特幣|比特幣]]和相关知识产权交予{{en-link|戴夫·克萊曼|Dave Kleiman}}遺屬<ref>[https://www.coindesk.com/judge-recommends-ruling-in-favor-of-kleiman-in-craig-wright-case?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=coindesk&utm_term=&utm_content=&utm_campaign=Organic%20 Judge Recommends Ruling in Favor of Kleiman in Craig Wright Case]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://modernconsensus.com/cryptocurrencies/bitcoin/exclusive-interview-with-craig-wright-just-after-ordered-to-pay-5-billion-in-bitcoin/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: First interview with Craig Wright after judge orders him to pay $5 billion in bitcoin |accessdate=2019-08-31 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230930/https://modernconsensus.com/cryptocurrencies/bitcoin/exclusive-interview-with-craig-wright-just-after-ordered-to-pay-5-billion-in-bitcoin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

